name: Imperial Domination (V)
Lore: 'When Vader''s forces impose the New Order upon a region, Rebel resources and lifelines are quickly eliminated.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. If your non-Imperial character (or [Independent Starship] starship) on table, this Effect lost. Unless you occupy fewer locations than opponent: if you initiate or win a battle, retrieve an Imperial; and, during battle, may take an Imperial just drawn for destiny into hand to cancel and redraw that destiny. (Immune to Alter.)',
